smol is a minimal blogging theme for Hugo.
Real-life example can be found at https://bajok.kretes.xyz
This is a fork of the original theme created by colorchestra - https://github.com/colorchestra/smol

Pros:
- Pure HTML/CSS
- Default dark theme
- No JavaScript
- No Google spyware or tracking of any kind

Installation:
Clone repository into themes directory inside of the hugo project.
Set the theme parameter to "smol" in the config file.
Add the following lines to the config file to make use of entries in the header and footer sections.

# Parameters
[params]
    subtitle = "Your blog subtitle goes here!"
    dateFmt = "02.01.2006 15:04"

# Header
[menu]
  [[menu.main]]
        identifier = "posts"
        name = "Posts"
        url = "/posts/"
        weight = 1 

  [[menu.main]]
        identifier = "categories"
        name = "Categories"
        url = "/categories/"
        weight = 2 

  [[menu.main]]
        identifier = "tags"
        name = "Tags"
        url = "/tags/"
        weight = 3

# Footer
  [[menu.footer]]
        name = "Github"
        url = "https://github.com/example"
        weight = 1 

    [[menu.footer]]
        name = "Mastodon"
        url = "https://example.com/@user"
        weight = 2 

    [[menu.footer]]
        name = "Imprint"
        url = "/imprint"
        weight = 3 

